Program: Free Thinking
Title: Colour: Sean Scully, Jamie Ward, Caroline Cox
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b046cs01
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 22 Dec 2014
Philip Dodd talks to the celebrated abstract artist, Sean Scully and neuroscientist Jamie Ward and fashion expert Caroline Cox explore our perception of colour. Producer: Zahid Warley Sean Scully: Kind of Red Installation view, Timothy Taylor Gallery, London, June 2014 Copyright, Sean Scully. Photo by Todd White Fine Art Photography You can download this programme by searching in the Arts and Ideas podcasts for the broadcast date. First broadcast June 2014. Show less